@startuml sequence_diagram_import
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram Import Data Excel\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran DBD

actor "Petugas" as User
participant "Halaman\nImport" as Page
participant "Controller\nImport" as Controller
participant "Python API\n(Flask)" as API
database "Database" as DB

User -> Page : Buka halaman Import
activate Page

Page --> User : Tampilkan form upload

User -> Page : Pilih file Excel
User -> Page : Klik tombol Upload

Page -> Page : Validasi format file\n(.xlsx)

Page -> Controller : Upload file
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller : Simpan file sementara
Controller -> API : POST /import\n{file_path}
activate API

API -> API : Load Excel dengan Pandas\npd.read_excel()
API -> API : Validasi kolom data
API -> API : Preprocessing data

loop Untuk setiap baris data
    API -> API : Parse data pasien
    API -> API : Validasi nilai
    API -> DB : INSERT INTO pasien_dbd
    activate DB
    DB --> API : Success
    deactivate DB
end

API -> API : Hitung jumlah berhasil/gagal
API --> Controller : Response\n{total, berhasil, gagal}
deactivate API

Controller -> DB : INSERT INTO log_aktivitas
Controller --> Page : Response hasil import
Page --> User : Tampilkan hasil:\n- Total data diproses\n- Berhasil diimport\n- Gagal diimport

deactivate Controller
deactivate Page

@enduml
